  "title": "突发：三大史上最大 IPO 迎来坏消息",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/breaking-bad-news-for-three-of-the",
  "date": "2026-05-29 03:40:00",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><span>Scoop from Madison Mills at Axios, reinforcing </span><a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/garymarcus/p/if-enough-other-companies-report?r=8tdk6&amp;utm_campaign=post-expanded-share&amp;utm_medium=web\">what I said here the other day</a><span>:</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bf253370-5251-486f-d462-abfd420de400/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27435a47-6b99-4b56-5501-4ce0bca38b00/public\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_808a654c-022a-42b6-9c8d-20e671767579_1504x1368.png 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27435a47-6b99-4b56-5501-4ce0bca38b00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>This is bad news for the AI industry, and fits well with what I warned about on Tuesday, adding in particular to the concerns from there that I circled below:</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_4f0eafa8-7f5b-407b-b987-36957dd0ec5e_1320x747.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p>One big reason why Anthropic is having a blowout quarter (aside from the massive one time subsidy that they got from SpaceX) is that companies have been “tokenmaxxing” for the last few months, encouraging employees to use GenAI as much possible, without much regard to payoff. That means lots of short-term revenue to Anthropic and OpenAI, but it never seemed like a sustainable idea to me:</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/garymarcus/status/2050009144846119068?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e896d385-456a-44b9-583e-edf1d3c7a300/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @GaryMarcus\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 1x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3be24ccf-5e2d-4967-a697-2e8865999b00/public 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260504162256_kPeRHI2z.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Gary Marcus, MIT PhD and NYU Professor Emeritus</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@GaryMarcus</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Tokenmaxxing is stupid. Change my mind?</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">12:27 AM · May 1, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">9.15K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">46 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">2 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">111 Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p><span>A month later, it </span><em>already </em><span>looks like the moment has passed; tokenmaxxing may have jacked up Anthropic’s second quarter, but it looks like it won’t last. Nobody is going to be comfortable accidentally burning half a billions of tokens in month. Budgets will tighten, especially when people realize just how costly agents (which burn orders of magnitudes more tokens) are.</span></p>\n   <p>Axios quotes Ali Ansari, CEO of a model training firm known as Micro1, as saying “The enterprise is undergoing a \"healthy swing\" away from AI overuse — or \"tokenmaxxing,\" the push to burn as many AI tokens as possible” – which means less revenue for Anthropic and others. Or lower prices and even more challenges in being profitable.</p>\n   <p>Consistent with the Axios quote, and the Uber concern’s I expressed a couple days ago, I am seeing more and more reports online like this:</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/hkarthik/status/2059318602332037351?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_zuVxC3sR.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_zuVxC3sR.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_zuVxC3sR.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_zuVxC3sR.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @hkarthik\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_zuVxC3sR.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_zuVxC3sR.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_zuVxC3sR.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Karthik Hariharan</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@hkarthik</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">The same conversation is happening across tech right now and many of us saw it coming. Tokens got burned for millions of dollars without any real significant ROI to show for it. The largest accounts with OpenAI and Anthropic subs have FDEs being thrown at them to retain the</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset elevatedTheme-fBklGV\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-padding-12 pc-boxShadow-none pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm sizing-border-box-DggLA4\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-8 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_Ew50qGxC.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_Ew50qGxC.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_Ew50qGxC.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_Ew50qGxC.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @edzitron\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_Ew50qGxC.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_Ew50qGxC.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_Ew50qGxC.jpg 3x\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Ed Zitron</span> <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@edzitron</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Uber’s COO has said that it’s getting “harder to justify” its AI costs because there was no way to show a link between AI spend and any meaningful increase in useful features. This is the first time I’ve seen a company say this directly. https://t.co/xUhZvtpwah</div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">4:59 PM · May 26, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">80.4K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">41 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">31 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">360 Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p><span>The second sentence— “</span><strong>Tokens got burned for millions of dollars without any real significant ROI to show for it</strong><span>” – might well turn out to be the epitaph for an era. </span></p>\n   <p>§</p>\n   <p>Just imagine what might happen to the economy and people’s retirement funds if these projections from FT are correct:</p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/askyoshik/status/2059849267725152285?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200257_O3_GeLW9.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_O3_GeLW9.jpg 2x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_O3_GeLW9.jpg 3x\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_O3_GeLW9.jpg\" alt=\"X avatar for @AskYoshik\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_O3_GeLW9.jpg 1x, https://image.jido.dev/20260528200258_O3_GeLW9.jpg 2x, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/774b4108-5474-470d-6230-ed96dc755800/public 3x\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Yoshik</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@AskYoshik</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">The AI numbers are starting to look very ugly. Even under \"best case\" assumptions, FT's own data shows Microsoft AI ROI at -9%, Google at -15%, Meta at -28%, Oracle at -35%. Only Amazon barely comes out positive. This is exactly why I keep comparing this to the dot-com era.</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset bg-black-dCpgGg outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 container-aGHQ9p\">\n      <img src=\"https://pbs.substack.com/media/HJYN6w3bwAAVxpa.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image-c_FmAR\">\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">4:08 AM · May 28, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">97.3K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">109 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">340 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1.46K Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p>And it could get worse, if tokenmaxxing is indeed a fad whose time has already begun to pass.</p>\n   <p>Brace for bailouts.</p>\n   <p></p>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文认为，'Tokenmaxxing'（无差别消耗 AI Token）的时代正在终结，因为企业几乎看不到投资回报，这威胁到了 Anthropic 和 OpenAI 等主要 AI 公司的收入模式。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文认为，'Tokenmaxxing'（无差别消耗 AI Token）的时代正在终结，因为企业几乎看不到投资回报，这威胁到了 Anthropic 和 OpenAI 等主要 AI 公司的收入模式。",
  "summary": "Gary Marcus 分析了 Axios 近期的一篇报道及其他信号，指出企业 AI 支出正发生重大转变。他认为，'Tokenmaxxing'（即公司鼓励大量消耗 AI Token 却缺乏明确商业理由的做法）正在迅速消退。其驱动力在于缺乏可证明的 ROI，Uber 的 COO 质疑 AI 成本，以及有报道称数百万美元花在 Token 上却回报甚微。Marcus 将此与更广泛的财务担忧联系起来，引用 FT 数据显示微软和谷歌等大型科技公司的 AI ROI 为负。他警告称，这种曾暂时提振 Anthropic 等公司收入的趋势不可持续，将导致预算收紧、价格下降，并可能给 AI 行业带来财务困境，这与互联网泡沫有相似之处。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "'Tokenmaxxing'的做法正在终结，因为企业未能从 AI 投资中获得回报。",
      "explanation": "那些鼓励大量消耗 AI Token 的公司如今正在收紧预算，因为缺乏显著 ROI 的问题日益凸显，这导致了一种'健康的转变'，远离过度使用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "微软和谷歌等大型科技公司的 AI 投资预计将出现负 ROI。",
      "explanation": "文章引用的《金融时报》数据显示，即使在最乐观的情况下，微软、谷歌、Meta 和甲骨文的 AI ROI 也深度为负，只有亚马逊勉强持平。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Tokenmaxxing 的终结威胁着 Anthropic 和 OpenAI 等领先 AI 公司的收入模式。",
      "explanation": "这些公司曾受益于 Token 消耗的短期激增，但随着预算收紧和焦点转向 ROI，它们的收入来源面临风险，可能导致价格下降和盈利能力受损。"
